12578static int32_T c1_div_nzp_s32(SFc1_GCU_Model_genCodeInstanceStruct



12579  *chartInstance, int32_T c1_numerator, int32_T c1_denominator, uint32_T



12580  c1_ssid_src_loc, int32_T c1_offset_src_loc, int32_T c1_length_src_loc)



12581{



12582  int32_T c1_quotient;



12583  uint32_T c1_absNumerator;



12584  uint32_T c1_absDenominator;



12585  boolean_T c1_quotientNeedsNegation;



12586  uint32_T c1_tempAbsQuotient;



12587  (void)chartInstance;



12588  (void)c1_ssid_src_loc;



12589  (void)c1_offset_src_loc;



12590  (void)c1_length_src_loc;



12591  if (c1_numerator < 0) {



12592    c1_absNumerator = ~(uint32_T)c1_numerator + 1U;



12593  } else {



12594    c1_absNumerator = (uint32_T)c1_numerator;



12595  }



12596



12597  if (c1_denominator < 0) {



12598    c1_absDenominator = ~(uint32_T)c1_denominator + 1U;



12599  } else {



12600    c1_absDenominator = (uint32_T)c1_denominator;



12601  }



12602



12603  c1_quotientNeedsNegation = ((c1_numerator < 0) != (c1_denominator < 0));



12604  c1_tempAbsQuotient = c1_absNumerator / c1_absDenominator;



12605  if (c1_quotientNeedsNegation) {

16577void c1_GCU_Model_genCode_method_dispatcher(SimStruct *S, int_T method, void



16578  *data)



16579{



16580  switch (method) {



16581   case SS_CALL_MDL_START:



16582    mdlStart_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(S);



16583    break;



16584



16585   case SS_CALL_MDL_SET_WORK_WIDTHS:



16586    mdlSetWorkWidths_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(S);



16587    break;



16588



16589   case SS_CALL_MDL_PROCESS_PARAMETERS:



16590    mdlProcessParameters_c1_GCU_Model_genCode(S);



16591    break;



16592



16593   default:



16594    /* Unhandled method */



16595    sf_mex_error_message("Stateflow Internal Error:\n"



16596                         "Error calling c1_GCU_Model_genCode_method_dispatcher.\n"



16597                         "Can't handle method %d.\n", method);



16598    break;



16599  }



16600}
